name: Expansion
summary:
The Galaxy is celebrating the Lunar New Year!
We are excited to announce a major update to Expansion VR, our popular virtual reality game, just in time for Lunar New Year!

Get into the shoes of a tactical warlord genius. Strategize, explore, and conquer as you build your own intergalactic empire. Engage in ultimate warfare and venture beyond the observable universe. Mastermind crucial decision-making and employ indirect control of units, relying on your strategic brilliance to outwit...
